== English ==

== Noun ==

(Plural ''truffles'')

*1  (''Biology'') A type of fleshy, [[ascomycetous]], edible [[fungi]], chiefly of the genus Tuber. Found underground on or near the roots of trees and are valued as a delicacy within certain cultures.

*2 (''Food'') A form of chocolate confectionary, made with a mix of chopped nuts. Often rolled into balls and covered with [[cocoa]] powder. Dessert or sweet served typically in [[European]] countries.